    "• None of the adversarial AI attack types in the dataset in Table 6 could be classified under the lateral movement, command and control, exfiltration, and impact stages of the MITRE ATT&CK Framework.The analysis of adversarial AI cyberattacks in Fig. 3 has several implications for both theory and practical cybersecurity considerations.",
